                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;So the difference is that I am doing a left inclusive join and then right exclusive using UNION &lt;i&gt;ALL&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/1422085/pavle-lekic&quot; title=&quot;972 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Pavle Lekic&lt;/a&gt;
